import TableWidget from './table/table-widget'
import LineChartWidget from './line-chart/line-chart-widget'
import BarChartWidget from './bar-chart/bar-chart-widget'
import PieChartWidget from './pie-chart/pie-chart-widget'
import DonutChartWidget from './donut-chart/donut-chart-widget'
import AreaChartWidget from './area-chart/area-chart-widget'

import TableWidgetSettings from './table/table-widget-settings'
import LineChartWidgetSettings from './line-chart/line-chart-widget-settings'
import BarChartWidgetSettings from './bar-chart/bar-chart-widget-settings'
import PieChartWidgetSettings from './pie-chart/pie-chart-widget-settings'
import DonutChartWidgetSettings from './donut-chart/donut-chart-widget-settings'
import AreaChartWidgetSettings from './area-chart/area-chart-widget-settings'

export {
  LineChartWidget,
  TableWidget,
  BarChartWidget,
  PieChartWidget,
  DonutChartWidget,
  AreaChartWidget,
  TableWidgetSettings,
  LineChartWidgetSettings,
  BarChartWidgetSettings,
  PieChartWidgetSettings,
  DonutChartWidgetSettings,
  AreaChartWidgetSettings
}
